{"TopicId":204063,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Lander Spins For no Reason","CreatedByName":"Mr. Beantown","CreatedById":213114,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-27T22:30:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mr. Beantown","CreatedById":213114,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-27T22:30:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy moon (minmus/mun) lander rotates for no reason. I see no reason why it would do this though (I cannot figure out how to post image from files)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-28T06:29:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake sure your joystick is zeroed, and hit alt-X to remove any trim settings you might have accidentally applied.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr. Beantown","CreatedById":213114,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-28T13:16:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt only starts rotating when there is no \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, and also I use keyboard and mouse, but I\u0027ll try anyway\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FleshJeb","CreatedById":111640,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-28T23:39:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224011054\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221627478179\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022213114\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mr. Beantown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Mr. Beantown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt only starts rotating when there is no \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, and also I use keyboard and mouse, but I\u0027ll try anyway\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrim only works when \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E is off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr. Beantown","CreatedById":213114,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-29T01:01:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nok thanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}